name: I know this monster
description:
You can live a thousand lives in one lifetime. Your own image gets confused and eventually becomes zero. And so you sit in a house with no address and you don't reject the monster inside you. You literally accept it.
The photo is from where I live now. It's a cabin in the mountains on the edge of the village. Magic and a thousand stories happen here. It's a home for adults abandoned by their parents. It's our separate universe with no way out and no way in.
